source.name: Payroll Report - End Date 3/28/2012
source.description: Bi-Weekly report of monies disbursed to Senate employees. The report is issued by the Secretary of the Senate and is available as both a .csv file and it's original PDF format. The Report includes fields for the employee name, the employing office, city of employment, the employee title, the employee biweekly or hourly rate (whichever applies), the employee payroll type, the pay period, the pay period's beginning and end date, the check date and the employing legislative entity.
